{"tid":2250402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲比沙卡「偷食」連加特前度 還被笑：技術差...","createTime":"2020-10-20T05:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T10:04:18.000Z","uid":147522,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac002eb25239d10c0bf21b3e73161e52d9ae05d","tid":2250402,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:38:44.000Z","msg":"　　曼聯最近有點亂，先是格連活特（Mason Greenwood）在國家隊期間約炮被當事女生揭發，如今紅魔主力後衛雲比沙卡又被曝料出軌醜聞。<br />\n<br />\n　　一位Instagram名叫marlie的女生現身曬照，爆料了雲比沙卡（Aaron Wan-Bissaka）和自己的親密過往。她言稱比沙卡和自己有兩性關係，還「抽水」了雲比沙卡「技術太差」。<br />\n<br />\n　　此外，她還表示，雲比沙卡曾告訴她，自己快要當父親了，但他不想要這個孩子。而這個孩子的母親，是一位不知名的女性。<br />\n<br />\n　　值得一提的，雲比沙卡此前有公開的女友，這意味著他的行為是出軌。而據Twitter上的多個大V稱，雲比沙卡出軌的對象，還是連加特（Jesse Lingard）的前任女友。<br />\n<br />\n　　直到目前，雲比沙卡的出軌傳聞，還保持在Twitter英國區熱搜榜第二名的位置。"},{"pid":"f4e76df7782f38837d4ac501afef90a839978a18","tid":2250402,"uid":156321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"awb咁嘅樣都...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d93a297c4f19172bdbb624b3cca1d784bf40a7d","tid":2250402,"uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SMrg2Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8SMrg2Q.jpg&h=db83eccc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kf22zPx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKf22zPx.jpg&h=91b1f903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eb1eebe054c63bf5a4895b5e11882f553d1474b","tid":2250402,"uid":20317,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"563fd35f2131a34cb892a7e78a7f193304e56bb8","tid":2250402,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb1eebe054c63bf5a4895b5e11882f553d1474b","tid":2250402,"uid":20317,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"f4e76df7782f38837d4ac501afef90a839978a18","tid":2250402,"uid":156321,"l